n class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">r</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">（</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.045em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.045em;">c</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">）</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> （图中的“鲍勃”）。与正常处理相比，产出没有变化。</li><li>在<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="L_2"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">L</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>层：模型输出<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="R_1(C_2)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">R</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">（</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.045em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.045em;">C</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">）</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> （“ Paris”）。这是请求修补最强的层。修补的残差流仅包含有关请求的信息；在修补的输出中没有明显的有关上下文的信息。</li><li>从<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="L_3"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">第</span></span></span><span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">3</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>层到最后一层：模型输出<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="R_1(C_1)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">R</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">（</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.045em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.045em;">C</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">）</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> （“伦敦”）。修补的残差流包含输入1上的任务实例的答案。修补实验等效于在输入1上进行硬编码。</li></ol><p>通常，请求点最有效的<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="L_2"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">L</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">第2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>层取决于任务： </p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uCuvFKnvzwh34GuX3/wqxaj9rfhydolkcly8gn"></p><p>没有明确的全球模式，但是我们可以从这些图中进行两个观察：</p><ul><li>归纳任务仅包括从上下文中重复字符串。它的请求表示（即模型应在上下文中寻找的前缀编码）似乎比涉及更复杂请求的其他任务更早地形成。</li><li>与其他模型相比，Llama 2 70b提出了一个奇特的内部组织。无论任务是什么任务，请求表示形式都在相同的狭窄层范围内形成（另请参阅右侧的跨层修补的结果）。似乎不依赖于输入中表面级别的变化的明显界定区域的体力很大。目前尚不清楚这是由于其大小或其他混杂因素所致。</li></ul><h3><strong>效果有多强？</strong></h3><p>换句话说，与在没有干预的情况下预测正确答案相比，该模型如何预测<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="R_1(C_2)=\text{“Paris&quot;}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">R</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">（</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.045em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.045em;">C</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">）</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mtext MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">“巴黎”</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ？ </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uCuvFKnvzwh34GuX3/ycfxc2coine1vwbtokje"><figcaption>白色区域是模型无法解决任务的设置（精度&lt;70％）。</figcaption></figure><p>我们通过将0设置为0设置为通过在给定上下文中回答一个随机问题的模型输出的概率来归一化，例如，如果有3个可能的问题要问有关故事，那么随机猜测给出了概率。 1设置为未经干预的模型的平均近代令牌概率。</p><p>在106个模型任务对中的98个中，修补的模型输出<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="R_1(C_2)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">R</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">（</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.045em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.045em;">c</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">）</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，超过70％的归一化基线令牌概率。在设置的56/106中，修补的模型输出<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="m